entries.femaleVariant: Have you ever done something like that?
Do not worry about me. 2023, 2051, 2070 – that was a bad one – all natural fluctuations in the market.
Three times. Sometimes, to win, you must go back to start.
Do not make things complicated. People are greedy and power-hungry.
But I-I don't want to lose my job. I can't lose my job.
At worst, they will transfer you. But you have much to gain from the chaos.
